sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP (mTLS)
    participant LLMJudge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP (mTLS)
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM / OpenAI LLM<br/>HTTP

    Note over HF,S3: Startup: Model Loading
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        S3->>HF: KServe Storage Initializer<br/>downloads model files<br/>AWS credentials
        Note over HF: Model loaded to /mnt/models<br/>Auto-detect architecture:<br/>SequenceClassification or GraniteForCausalLM
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in Detection (Regex/FileType/Custom)
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Orchestrator->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext :8080<br/>{"detectors": {"pii_detector": {}}, "content": "..."}
        Note over BuiltIn: Registry dispatches to<br/>detector function (regex,<br/>file_type, or custom)
        BuiltIn-->>Orchestrator: [{"detection": "pii", "score": 0.95, ...}]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace ML Detection
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Orchestrator->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP mTLS (Istio) :8000<br/>{"content": "..."}
        Note over HF: Local PyTorch inference<br/>AutoModelForSequenceClassification<br/>or GraniteForCausalLM risk scan<br/>(harm, bias, jailbreak, profanity, ...)
        HF-->>Orchestrator: [{"detection": "toxicity", "score": 0.87, ...}]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Orchestrator->>LLMJudge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP mTLS (Istio) :8000<br/>{"content": "...", "detector_params": {"metrics": ["safety"]}}
        LLMJudge->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext<br/>Evaluation prompt (Jinja2 template)
        vLLM-->>LLMJudge: LLM evaluation response
        LLMJudge-->>Orchestrator: [{"detection": "safety", "score": 0.92, ...}]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,LLMJudge: Flow 3b: LLM Judge Generation Evaluation
    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Orchestrator->>LLMJudge: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>HTTP mTLS (Istio) :8000<br/>{"prompt": "...", "generated_text": "..."}
        LLMJudge->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Prompt+Response pair evaluation
        vLLM-->>LLMJudge: LLM evaluation response
        LLMJudge-->>Orchestrator: [{"detection": "helpfulness", "score": 0.78, ...}]
    end
